---
title: Roast Pork Belly & Creamy Garlic Sauce with Potato Mash & Baby Rainbow Carrots
description: Get ready for a bit of bliss on a fork because it’s roasted pork belly tonight. The creamy garlic sauce poured over the pork and a serving of nutty rainbow carrots really helps to send your tastebuds to their happy place.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/65cc57f23dbfdc1d2e0c5573-633f21b5.jpeg
